Description: Backport a core NVIDIA-owned kthread FIFO workqueue drain
 Replace the core nvidia module's schedule_work()/flush_scheduled_work()
 compatibility macros with a module-owned FIFO kthread executor and explicit
 status-returning flush/shutdown operations. This avoids the Linux system-wide
 workqueue flush warning while keeping nvidia-modeset out of scope.
Author: Codex <codex@openai.com>
Forwarded: not-needed




